{
  "chapter": 70,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十回\"死里求生\"中，铜先生因小鱼儿逗侍女发笑而暴怒，竟将圆脸少女一掌打死。小鱼儿怒斥其残忍，铜先生却反手传授三招破解移花宫武功的黄绢。铁萍姑揭示被杀少女是其亲妹，为报小鱼儿为妹争辩之恩，趁铜先生入定之际带他逃亡。二人经古刹复壁地道进入山腹洞穴，发现古人刻的箭头实为回庙之路而非出路。小鱼儿凭智慧判断箭头方向，与铁萍姑在黑暗洞穴中相互扶持前行，两人感情在生死逃亡中逐渐升温。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "但你却为他笑了，是么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "你出去吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "求求你……求求你饶婢子一命，婢子下次再也不敢了。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "饶她一命？你……你难道要杀了她？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "杀，倒也不必，只不过割下她的舌头，要她以后永远也笑不出。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "她只不过笑了笑，你就要割下她的舌头？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这只能怪你，你本不该逗她笑的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我只不过说了个笑话给她听，你……你何必吃醋！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你打我没关系，但千万不能因为这件事罚她。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你竟然为她说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这件事本不能怪她，要怪也只能怪我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好……好！你宁可要我打你，也不愿我罚她，你……你倒也和你那爹爹一样，是个多情种子！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你……你竟杀了她！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我杀了她，她再也不能偷偷和你逃走。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你疯了么？她几时要和我偷偷逃走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "等你们逃走时，我再杀她，便已迟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你疯了，你简直疯了……我本以为你脾气虽然冷酷，却并不是个狠毒残忍的人，谁知你竟能对一个女子下此毒手。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "像你这样的武功，最多也不过能接得住花无缺五十招而已，我本以为你还可与他一拼，谁知你竟如此令我失望。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我能接得住他多少招，关你屁事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里有三招可以破解'移花宫'武功的招式，你若能在这三个月里将它练成，纵不能胜了花无缺，至少也可多挡他几招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你……你是什么意思？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你究竟是要花无缺杀我，还是要我杀花无缺？你究竟有什么毛病？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这一生，已注定了要有悲惨的结局。无论你杀了花无缺，还是花无缺杀了你，都是一样的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两样菜不辣的，你吃不吃都随便你。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还吃得下么？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "现在说话没关系，没有人会来的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我肚子都快撑破，连一只蚂蚁都吞不下了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你最好还是多吃些，这两天，我们只怕都没有东西吃了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因我们现在就要开始逃，在逃亡的途中，绝不会有东西吃的，甚至连水都喝不到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "逃？……你是说逃走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我方才拼命的吃，就为的是要有力气逃走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但铜先生……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "现在正是他入定的时候，至少在两个时辰之内，不会到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你能确定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他这习惯数十年来从未改过。据说十多年前，也有个身分和我一样的女子，就是在这时候，带了一个人逃走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "难怪他方才那般愤怒，原来他就是怕历史重演……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道方才被他杀死的那女孩子是谁？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "那莫非是你的……你的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她就是我嫡亲的妹妹。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "对不起，我方才本不该逗她笑的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我妹子跟了他七年，他为了那么小的事，也能下得了毒手，而你与我妹子素不相识，反而为她争辩，甚至不惜为她拼命……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你就是为了这个原因，所以才冒险救我的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但经过十多年前的那次事件，他防守得必定十分严密，我们能逃得出去么？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "若是在他的禁宫中，我们实在连一分逃走的机会都没有，但这里，却只不过是他临时歇脚的地方。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "何况，这地方不但是我找到的，而且是我布置的，我们虽不是一定能逃得出去，但好歹也得试一试，那总比在这里等死的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这里究竟是什么地方？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这是个庙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里本是个冷清清的古刹，经过我们一整天的布置，才变成这样子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你们本事可真不小。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "但时间宝贵得很，我们为何还不走？你若是想聊天，等我们逃出去之后，时间还多着哩。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我们要等人来收去这些碗筷后才能走，否则立刻就会被人发觉，我们已不在这屋子里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "不错，我小地方总是疏忽，好像每个女孩子都比我细心得多。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你认得的女孩子很多么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我真希望能少认得几个……你呢？你认得的男孩子……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我一个都不认得。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你现在总算已认得我了，我姓江，叫江小鱼，你呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不妨叫我铁萍姑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你也姓铁？为什么姓铁的女孩子这么多……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你妹妹已死了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你伤心么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "我若伤心，你开心么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你也可以出去了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你说我可以出去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你自然知道我说的是你，你为何还不走？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "谁叫我走的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你现在已可以换班了，我叫你去休息休息还不好？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不愿意她走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "她走了最好，她那副晚娘面孔，我已瞧腻了，你虽然也未必比她好看多少，但换个新的总比旧的好，我天生是喜新厌旧的脾气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你眼睛若敢盯着我，我就挖出你眼珠子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你嘴里虽说不愿我瞧你，心里却是愿意的，说不定你还希望我能抱一抱你、亲一亲你，否则你为何定要将她调走，自己留在这里？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你敢对我如此说话？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你可不是雌老虎，我为何不敢？我还想咬你一口哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_yi_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "紫衣少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你莫以为我不能杀你，我至少么可打断你——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你不怕别人发现……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "时机难再，我只好冒一冒险了。何况，在这里的人，都不会关心别人的事，她就算三天不露面，也不会有人找她的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "快跟着我来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "想不到庙里居然也会有复壁地道，你是什么时候发现的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我收拾这间屋子时，已发现了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "据我猜想，这古刹乃是五胡作乱时所建，那时流寇盗贼横行，人命更贱于猪狗，很多人都削发出家，借以避祸，但庙宇中也非安全之地，所以寺僧才建了这些复壁地道，以躲避散兵流寇的杀掠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你的确和我所认识的其他女孩子有些不同，你有头脑……这世上有头有脑的女孩子，已越来越少了，而且有些人就算有头脑，却偏偏懒得去用它，她们总认为只要有张漂亮的脸就够了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但这却只能怪男人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因男人都不喜欢有头脑的女孩子，他们都生怕女孩子比自己强，所以越是聪明的女孩子，就越是要装得愚笨软弱。男人既然天生就觉得自己比女人强，喜欢保护女人，女人为何不让他们多伤些脑筋，多吃些苦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "如此说来，愚笨的倒是男人了，……但你连一个男人也不认得，又怎会对男人了解得这么清楚？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "女人天生就能了解男人的，但男人却永远不会了解女人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这话倒的确不错，一个男人若自以为能了解女人，他受苦的日子就不远了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这庙宇的复壁难道是连着山腹的么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "在这种地方，铜先生就算有通天的本事，想找到咱们也不容易。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但我们一心要走出去，只怕也不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你……你难道也不知道出去的路？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我当然不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "那么你……你为什么说咱们可以逃得出去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只要有路，我们自然就有逃出去的希望。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "姑娘你未免将事情瞧得太简单了。你可知道，山腹中的这些洞隙，有的根本是没有路通出去的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "也还有的是可以通得出去的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "纵然有路，但这些洞穴简直比诸葛亮的八阵图还要复杂诡秘，有时你在里面兜上三个月的圈子，到最后才发现自己又回到原来的地方。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "据我所知，古往今来，被困死在这山腹里的冤死鬼，若是聚在一起，阎王老子的森罗殿只怕也要被挤破了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "既是如此，再加两个也不多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你——你难道不着急？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若着急，现在回去，还来得及。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你别生气，我并没有怪你，只不过……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你以为我不知道这里的危险？但无论如何，我们总有一半的机会能逃出去，这总比坐在那里等死好得多，是么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "早知道你这么生气，那些话我就不说了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我真想不到你竟是个如此奇怪的人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我也真未想到，你的脾气竟这么大。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "现在我们既然已可走出去了，你为何站着不动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你若沿着这箭头走，再走片刻，就可以见到铜先生了，但我可不愿再见到他那副尊容。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这些箭头难道不是指路的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "箭头虽然是指路的，但指的却绝不是出去的路。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怎知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "这些箭头，必定是以前庙里的和尚刻上去的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "他们也为的是怕迷失路途，被困死在这里，所以才刻这些箭头的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "他们为了躲避流寇，所以才躲到这里，等他们知道流寇走了之后，你想他们要到什么地方去呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "自然是回到庙里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，这些箭头指的一定是回庙去的路，他们只不过是想在这山腹里躲避一时，又怎会去标明出路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我早已说过，你是个很有头脑的女孩子，你终于明白了。我看你方才想不通，只怕也是故意装出来的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你带路吧。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "所以越是聪明的女孩子，就越是要装得愚笨软弱，所以你现在就要我多伤脑筋、多出些力……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这件事就算是你对了，也没什么了不起。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我就是要你脸红、生气，你生起气来，才真正像是个女孩子，我实在受不了你那副冷冰冰的样子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的脸真红了么？我实在连自己都不知道脸红时是什么样子，这只怕还是我生平第一次……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这样走，能走得出去么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我虽不知能否走得出去，但这样走，至少距离那庙宇越来越远了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "现在，咱们看来只有碰运气了，索性闭着眼睛往前走吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "一个人的心若是要跳，谁也没法子叫它停住。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我们歇歇再走吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "绝不能歇下来，一歇，就再也休想走得动了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但我……我现在已……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你想，我们在这千古以来都少有人来过的神秘洞穴里拉着手散步，这是多么美，多么风流浪漫的事，别人一辈子都不会有这种机会，我们为何不多享受享受？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只可惜我……我不是你心上的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "谁说不是的，此时此刻，除了你之外，世上还有和我更亲近的人么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    }
  ],
